<hw>Scarce"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch. &
Engin.)</fld> <def>An offset where a wall or bank of earth, etc.,
retreats, leaving a shelf or footing.</def>⟦br⟧
